    <title>Fiesta Jazz </title>
    <link>https://www.pbsfm.org.au/program/fiesta-jazz</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since October 2000, Fiesta Jazz has been playing Latin jazz from traditional, instrumental and vocal Afro-Caribbean, Spanish and Brazilian jazz, as well as Latin-influenced fusion played by non-Latin musicians, along with fusions of jazz and Latin American folk rhythms.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a Venezuelan myself, the music expresses my Latin American and Spanish culture.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    <language>en</language>
    <category>Latin, jazz &amp; fusion</category>
